cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RA response window to an invalid value of 999 will cause random access response timing errors and prevent UE initial access.
du.explanation_zh: 將 RA 回應視窗設定為無效值 999 會導致隨機接入回應定時錯誤，並阻止 UE 初始接入。
